<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62db5649-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s5126"><num value="5126">§ 5126.</num><heading> Mandatory application of sections 5102 and 5124</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Notwithstanding <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s5125">section 5125 of this title</ref>, sections 5102 and 5124 of this title shall apply to—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62db564a-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s5126/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> all Indian tribes,</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62db564b-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s5126/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> all lands held in trust by the United States for Indians, and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62db564c-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s5126/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> all lands owned by Indians that are subject to a restriction imposed by the United States on alienation of the rights of the Indians in the lands.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id62db564d-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/301/s3/a">Pub. L. 101–301, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="1990-05-24">May 24, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/207">104 Stat. 207</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id62db564e-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id62db564f-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id62db5650-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s478–1">section 478–1 of this title</ref> prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
